premise_source_doc_sentence: Neha Kakkar is a global playback singer .
She competed on the television reality show Indian Idol season 2 in 2006 .
In 2008 , she launched the album Neha The Rock Star with music composed by Meet Brothers .

Her other work includes the songs `` Sunny Sunny '' , `` Manali Trance '' and Aao Raja with singer Honey Singh , `` Dhating Naach '' , `` London Thumakda '' and `` Hanju '' with singer `` Meiyang Chang '' , Patt Lainge with singer Gippy Grewal .
The track has been sung by Neha Kakkar and Gippy Grewal and is the 3rd song released from the film Loveshhuda by Tips Industries Limited , starring Girish Kumar and Navneet Kaur Dhillon .
